com.sillysoft.lux.util
Class CountryPathStack

java.lang.Object
  com.sillysoft.lux.util.CountryStack
      com.sillysoft.lux.util.CountryPathStack

public class CountryPathStack
extends CountryStack

This is an implementation of a stack that stores CountryPath objects. You can add to the top, or add with a value. If added with a (int) value then the the added item will be sorted into the correct place in the stack.

You can pop from the front.
